<HEADLINE>
<P>
DAVID BOMBYK; PRESIDENT OF GEFFEN FILM CO. 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
David Bombyk, 36, president of Geffen Film Co., who was only 19 when he began 
his film career in Warner Bros.' story department. He became story editor for 
Kings Road Productions in Los Angeles, then joined Edward S. Feldman 
Productions as head of creative affairs in 1982. In 1984, he co-produced 
