thriller "The Hitchhiker." As an independent producer he developed motion 
picture properties for Walt Disney Productions and in 1986 joined Geffen, where 
he oversaw production of last year's hit film "Beetlejuice." In Los Angeles on 
Jan. 20 of the complications of AIDS. 
