<HEADLINE>
<P>
SOVIET TRAIN DERAILS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By from Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
MOSCOW 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A Soviet freight train derailed Friday in the Volga region, spilling 
concentrated acid but causing no injuries or damage, Tass said. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Wire 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA012989-0158 </DOCNO>
