<P>
Photo, Kenneth and Florine Beets with their favorite family photo -- one from 
1943, when Kenneth Jr. was a boy. Below, Florine holds photo of Kenneth Jr. 
taken about a year before his death. MARK BOSTER / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
